data.description: Exciting Opportunity Large Corner Lot: Embrace the chance to own a Stunning New 2-Story Home in the Deer Run - Swartz Creek Community! The sought-after 2009 sq ft plan boasts an inviting open kitchen adjoining a spacious great room, alongside a delightful dining area with a pantry. Revel in the kitchen's exquisite cabinets, and stainless-steel appliances, including a range, microwave, and dishwasher. Discover convenience with all bedrooms, as well as the laundry room, situated on the 2nd floor. The primary suite offers a private bathroom with dual vanity sinks and a walk-in closet, while three generously sized bedrooms share another full-sized bath. Enjoy the flexibility of a versatile loft space and a convenient walk-in laundry room on the second floor. This appealing plan also features a 2.5-car garage. Don't let this opportunity slip away!
